---
---
<section id="pricing" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border scroll-mt-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">Pricing</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">They charge $129/mo to monitor.<br/>We charge $29/mo to <span class="text-accent">fix it</span>.</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Every plan includes full scoring, file generation, and CI integration. No feature gates on the stuff that matters.</p>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-14">

			<!-- Starter -->
			<div class="pricing-card animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="pricing-card__inner p-8 flex flex-col">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Starter</p>
					<div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
						<span class="text-5xl font-bold text-text">$0</span>
						<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/month</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Try everything. No credit card.</p>

					<ul class="mt-8 space-y-3.5 flex-1">
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>1 site</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>3 dashboard scans / month</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>Full 36-criteria scoring</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>All 9 generated files</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>CLI — unlimited local usage</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>GitHub App + Action</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check">✓</span>13 framework plugins</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature pricing-feature--muted"><span class="pricing-dash">—</span>No history or trends</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature pricing-feature--muted"><span class="pricing-dash">—</span>No auto-rescan</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="https://app.aeorank.dev/sign-up" class="btn-secondary justify-center mt-8 !text-sm">Start Free</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Pro — highlighted -->
			<div class="pricing-card pricing-card--pro animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="pricing-card__inner p-8 flex flex-col relative">
					<div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
						<span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white bg-accent px-4 py-1 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-accent/25">Best Value</span>
					</div>

					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">Pro</p>
					<div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
						<span class="text-5xl font-bold text-text">$29</span>
						<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/month</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Full monitoring + fix generation. <span class="text-accent font-medium">4× cheaper than Otterly.</span></p>

					<ul class="mt-8 space-y-3.5 flex-1">
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span><strong>5 sites</strong></li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span><strong>50 scans / month</strong></li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>30-day score history + trends</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>Per-page scoring breakdown</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>Auto-rescan (daily / weekly / monthly)</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>PDF export + comparison view</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>Dimension trend charts</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--pro">✓</span>Everything in Starter</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="https://app.aeorank.dev/sign-up" class="btn-primary justify-center mt-8 !text-sm">Start Pro — $29/mo</a>
					<p class="text-text-muted text-[11px] text-center mt-2">Otterly charges $99/mo for this. Scrunch charges $500.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Agency / API -->
			<div class="pricing-card animate-on-scroll">
				<div class="pricing-card__inner p-8 flex flex-col">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#6366F1] uppercase tracking-wider">Agency</p>
					<div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
						<span class="text-5xl font-bold text-text">$99</span>
						<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/month</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-text-muted text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">For agencies managing client portfolios at scale.</p>

					<ul class="mt-8 space-y-3.5 flex-1">
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span><strong>50 sites</strong></li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span><strong>500 scans / month</strong></li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>REST API access</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>Bulk scan endpoints</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>Webhook notifications</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>Client-ready PDF reports</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>Priority support</li>
						<li class="pricing-feature"><span class="pricing-check pricing-check--api">✓</span>Everything in Pro</li>
					</ul>

					<a href="https://app.aeorank.dev/sign-up" class="btn-secondary justify-center mt-8 !text-sm" style="border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.3);">Start Agency — $99/mo</a>
					<p class="text-text-muted text-[11px] text-center mt-2">Scrunch charges $500/mo. Semrush charges $129+.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

		<!-- Competitor comparison strip -->
		<div class="mt-14 rounded-xl border border-border bg-white/[0.02] p-6 md:p-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
				<div>
					<p class="text-accent font-bold text-lg">AEOrank Pro</p>
					<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mt-1">$29<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/mo</span></p>
					<p class="text-green text-xs mt-1 font-medium">Score + Fix + Monitor</p>
				</div>
				<div class="opacity-50">
					<p class="text-text-muted font-medium text-sm">Otterly.ai</p>
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-muted mt-1">$99<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/mo</span></p>
					<p class="text-red text-xs mt-1">Monitor only</p>
				</div>
				<div class="opacity-50">
					<p class="text-text-muted font-medium text-sm">Scrunch AI</p>
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-muted mt-1">$500<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/mo</span></p>
					<p class="text-red text-xs mt-1">Monitor only</p>
				</div>
				<div class="opacity-50">
					<p class="text-text-muted font-medium text-sm">Semrush AI</p>
					<p class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-muted mt-1">$129<span class="text-text-muted text-sm">/mo</span></p>
					<p class="text-red text-xs mt-1">Monitor only</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="text-center text-text-muted text-xs mt-6">They charge more to tell you what's wrong. We charge less to fix it.</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Bottom note -->
		<div class="mt-10 text-center space-y-2">
			<p class="text-text-muted text-sm">The CLI, GitHub App, GitHub Action, and all 13 framework plugins are <strong class="text-text">free on every plan</strong> — including Starter.</p>
			<p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Cancel anytime · No contracts · 14-day money-back guarantee · Prices in USD</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.pricing-card {
		border-radius: 16px;
		position: relative;
	}

	.pricing-card__inner {
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
		height: 100%;
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
	}

	.pricing-card:hover .pricing-card__inner {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	.pricing-card--pro .pricing-card__inner {
		border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.3);
		background: linear-gradient(170deg, rgba(232,89,12,0.08) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 40%);
	}

	.pricing-card--pro:hover .pricing-card__inner {
		border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.5);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(232,89,12,0.15), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
	}

	.pricing-feature {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.pricing-feature--muted {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.pricing-check {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 1.25rem;
		height: 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-size: 0.625rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		background: rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
		color: #22C55E;
		border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2);
	}

	.pricing-check--pro {
		background: rgba(232,89,12,0.12);
		color: #E8590C;
		border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.25);
	}

	.pricing-check--api {
		background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12);
		color: #818CF8;
		border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
	}

	.pricing-dash {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 1.25rem;
		height: 1.25rem;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		opacity: 0.5;
	}
</style>
